{
  "texts": [
    "While this immediate recovery approach improved evaluation scores of the pruned model, it did not achieve performance gains over our standard method of fine-tuning only once after complete pruning.",
    "This might be due to overfitting caused by fine-tuning several times on the small in-domain dataset.",
    "Moreover, immediate recovery through fine-tuning after each pruning iteration is much more computationally intensive.",
    "In our main pruning experiments (cf.",
    "Section 3.3), we pruned only 8 layers based on layer importance evaluation."
  ]
}